    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board SK-J07 (700mm x 420mm)",
    "body_html": "<div data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"ProductItem-details-excerpt\" data-content-field=\"excerpt\" id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1686881405683_441\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>SeaKing SK-J07</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing SK-J07 and SK-K08 boast a sophisticated and durable design, featuring a sleek </span><span>appearance complemented by a spacious knife tray and storage sink. Available in white or black </span><span>gelcoat finishes, these bait boards are meticulously handcrafted using premium composite materials, </span><span>including a UV resistant PE plastic cutting board for lasting performance on the water. Designed to </span><span>combine elegance with functionality, these bait boards are perfect for anglers seeking a stylish yet </span><span>robust solution for their fishing needs. </span></p>\n<ul></ul>\n</div>",
